CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 17, 2010

[Cite as 05/17/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-2133.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-0001. State ex rel. Starr v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 09AP-267, 2009-Ohio-6568. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
